            "short_description": "Eve is a legal AI platform founded in 2023 and based in Redwood City, California. It provides AI-powered tools tailored for plaintiff law firms, enhancing workflows throughout the entire case lifecycle, from intake to resolution. The platform enables firms to automate repetitive tasks, allowing them to manage 3-4 times more cases and achieve significant revenue growth without increasing staff. Eve's technology processes over 200,000 cases annually and has helped firms recover more than $3.5 billion in settlements and judgments.\n\nEve's suite of tools includes features for case intake and evaluation, medical overviews, demand letter drafting, and discovery management. These capabilities lead to substantial productivity gains, enabling firms to focus on high-value work. With over 450 top plaintiff law firms as clients, Eve is committed to making high-quality legal representation more accessible, particularly in personal injury and labor & employment cases. The company has raised $164 million in funding, reflecting strong investor confidence in its mission and impact.",
